After building the BNp model from pathways, we extract the CPMs based on the procedure explained for simulations on synthetic networks. Since the network is fixed in this example, we randomly select 10 different sets of 5 conditional probabilities and assume that they are unknown. We run the experimental design simulations for 100 different assumed true values for each set of unknown probabilities. The length of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
